title: EnigmOn v1.5
description:
Do you like to solve brain-teasing riddles ?
Do you like to rack your brain on problems ?
Do you like to take up challenges about everything ?

So You'll love playing EnigmOn !

EnigmOn is a great enigmas game that use all the capacities and features of your Smartphone.
Just imagine all the possibilities !

Each detail is important, each sound, each picture even the littlest reference could be useful in order to help you to solve the enigmas.

Can you meet the Challenge ?!
Now it's your turn to play !

What's New:

Flyer for Enigm, the second opus of EnigmOn
Now you can find some help about enigmas on community blog. See home game, community link.
